{"tid":2121334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歐陽震華拍片教拍打養生　暴瘦模樣曝光引網民關注","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T13:25:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c615ad0677ee96d93f43295ff057a84ceb0e4285","tid":2121334,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"「收視福將」歐陽震華（Bobby）自從在今年1月拍攝完警匪劇《伙記辦大事》後，在4月就宣布離巢，結束與無綫電視38年之賓主關係，專注於內地發展。可能受疫情影響關係，歐陽震華近月只出演過內地節目《看我的生活》一集，與佘詩曼探討雪卵的話題。<br />\n<br />\n暫未有新劇拍的Bobby亦加入抖音市場Keep人氣，日前他就拍片親自示範幾招拍打經絡養生的方法，不少網民都留言稱Bobby消瘦不少，亦有人留言想念歐陽胖胖，當然亦有期待他的新劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200722/362661901332779008.jpeg/MW1qzUEg7zfIwL7Ejb4-smpNeT309PHItXwk4LV8JOA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200722%2F362661901332779008.jpeg%2FMW1qzUEg7zfIwL7Ejb4-smpNeT309PHItXwk4LV8JOA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=03d387b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200722/362661896626769920.jpeg/THZRPqwGcoTRNqrrEtEcgjGcEvqg0OEAiclKC4nJSgs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200722%2F362661896626769920.jpeg%2FTHZRPqwGcoTRNqrrEtEcgjGcEvqg0OEAiclKC4nJSgs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0ab47a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200722/362661903065026560.jpeg/RgHbme9wSqOLrKa3BwuZVemiJiwffGQer3otGq96LRo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200722%2F362661903065026560.jpeg%2FRgHbme9wSqOLrKa3BwuZVemiJiwffGQer3otGq96LRo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f0b272b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"452a081dea0b0f249c73aab4d53ccdc4486cc7c5","tid":2121334,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"頂冷帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"